# Doorways material override file
# This file stores Doorways-specific material settings outside Blender's .mtl file.
#
# Keep this file under source control.
# Blender may overwrite exported .mtl files, but it should not overwrite this file.
#
# Format:
#
# material MATERIAL_NAME
# tex_scale U_SCALE V_SCALE
# specular_strength VALUE
#
# The material name must match the Blender/MTL material name exactly.


